Saudi Arabia Museum of Contemporary Art is located in Riyadh, Al Diriyah Al Jadidah, temporarily at JAX District. The institution was conceived in 2023 by the Museums Commission, Ministry of Culture. SAMoCA’s mission is to foster creative transformation by providing a platform for local artists, promoting cultural exchange, and enriching the artistic landscape of the Kingdom.

name: تراثيات المملكة - للتحف والهدايا التراثية
description: Welcome to kingdom Heritage, a leading organization specializing in the creation and production of exquisite traditional gifts in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.
